00:43:50,678 --> 00:43:52,618
Hashtag Cha Bong Soo.

602
00:43:52,618 --> 00:43:55,568
Have another one. Another one. You must be tired.

603
00:43:55,568 --> 00:43:58,658
Gosh, Gong Hyung. My Gong Hyung.

