613
00:44:25,808 --> 00:44:28,238
- Sure, sounds good. 
 - Okay, got it.

614
00:44:28,238 --> 00:44:29,908
Shouldn't we go golfing sometime?

615
00:44:29,908 --> 00:44:31,838
I know.

