00:44:45,598 --> 00:44:50,088
So I'm an amazing cook, too.

620
00:44:50,088 --> 00:44:53,248
Tell me if you're craving anything.

621
00:44:53,248 --> 00:44:55,778
I can cook anything for you.

622
00:44:55,778 --> 00:45:00,108
Make soft tofu stew with clams, then.

623
00:45:01,278 --> 00:45:04,968
I'll taste it and decide if I'd hire you.

624
00:45:04,968 --> 00:45:06,618
Okay.

625
00:45:07,198 --> 00:45:09,528
Got it.

