00:45:33,948 --> 00:45:37,708
What's Gong Jin Dan doing here?

632
00:45:43,088 --> 00:45:47,478
 That country bumpkin looks just like Park Do Ra when she's like that. 

633
00:45:49,408 --> 00:45:54,088
 No, why am I looking at her here? 

634
00:46:00,468 --> 00:46:03,518
