635
00:46:03,518 --> 00:46:06,108
I'm here to cheer for Cha Bong Soo.

636
00:46:06,108 --> 00:46:08,218
I invested in this drama, too.

637
00:46:08,218 --> 00:46:11,388
By the way, what are you doing here?

638
00:46:11,388 --> 00:46:14,808
I'm here for work, too.

639
00:46:14,808 --> 00:46:18,048
I'll leave you to it, then, President Gong.

