00:46:23,348 --> 00:46:26,988
Is that actor named Do Do in this drama?

641
00:46:28,278 --> 00:46:30,818
I don't think I saw her on the list.

642
00:46:31,378 --> 00:46:35,058
Gosh. Good job, Ji Yeong. Here.

