722
00:51:33,788 --> 00:51:36,258
Because Soo Yeon told everyone.

723
00:51:37,258 --> 00:51:39,768
Is that true?

724
00:51:39,768 --> 00:51:43,498
Yes. I heard about it just today.

725
00:51:43,498 --> 00:51:48,688
That's why I'm telling you now that Pil Sung was an abandoned baby.

726
00:51:50,048 --> 00:51:54,238
Seon Yeong acting like that toward my wife is...

727
00:51:54,238 --> 00:51:56,338
because...

