00:51:59,548 --> 00:52:02,188
Seon Yeong was betrayed by her trusty friend.

730
00:52:02,188 --> 00:52:05,308
She must've been so shocked.

731
00:52:16,108 --> 00:52:17,928
Mom,

732
00:52:18,728 --> 00:52:23,018
Pil Sung's grandma apparently overheard

